      ],
      "content": "For those that are not familiar with AD deployment, see the <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>AD DS Deployment Guide<ept id=\"p1\">](https://technet.microsoft.com/library/cc753963)</ept> or <bpt id=\"p2\">[</bpt>Plan your AD FS deployment<ept id=\"p2\">](https://technet.microsoft.com/library/dn151324.aspx)</ept> as appropriate."
    },
