      ],
      "content": "<ph id=\"ph1\">&lt;a name=\"BKMK_FedReqVIPDIP\"&gt;</ph><ph id=\"ph2\">&lt;/a&gt;</ph>Federation server requirements for public and private IP addressing (dynamic IP vs. virtual IP)"
